Quickstrike:



Quickstrike looked at Black Arachnia, and took a small step to the 
side. He never seen so much affection from her. But be might as well 
go along with it. He missed her when she left the Predacons those 
long days ago. Was he ever so sore about it. They were back together 
now and it looked like it was for keeps.

He grabbed Black Arachnia around her shoulders firmly, but not hard. 
Respect was needed. 

"Sugar-bot, ya gotta tell me what's goin' on. Ya got uh plan wit' 
Megatron an' Hell Beast? Ah mean, ya really can't be on their side, 
right? Ah can't stand both of 'em. Megatron maybe uh little, but Hell 
Beast? No way. What's yer plan? Ah'm bein' left out in th' dark here, 
an' ah'm second in command." He raised his brows at her to let her 
know about his seriousness of it. His main expressions were in his 
optics. "An' why's KitKat actin' all high an' mighty?"
